sub_title: Legal Adviser - DLAPIL - Council of Europe
summary:
Lawyer specialised in Public International Law, with an interest for Human Rights and International Administrative Law.
Fluent in English and French.

Certificate in management (United Nations System Staff College) and currently attending a training in International Law Organizations (United Nations Institute for Training and Research).
